title: Reacting to our cringiest moments… exposing ourselves!
description:
This week on Fool Coverage, Manny and Laura tell their most cringe and embarrassing moments! Like Manny's infamous catwalk at the Marco Marco show, Laura wearing a nightgown on The Today Show, falling down the stairs at Beauty Con, Manny's disaster makeup artist brand deal, and much more!
Follow Laura on IG: @larlarlee
Follow Manny on IG: @mannymua733
